@apigateway = https://localhost:5001

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  AUTH
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get current user (me)
GET {{apigateway}}/api/v1/auth/user

### Update display name
PUT {{apigateway}}/api/v1/auth/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "John Smith"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  SESSIONS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get all sessions
GET {{apigateway}}/api/v1/sessions

### Get session by ID
GET {{apigateway}}/api/v1/sessions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Get session by code
GET {{apigateway}}/api/v1/sessions/by-code/AB12

### Create session
POST {{apigateway}}/api/v1/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mountain Trip",
  "displayName": "John"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  PARTICIPANTS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get participants
GET {{apigateway}}/api/v1/sessions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/participants

### Join session
POST {{apigateway}}/api/v1/sessions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "John"
}

### Leave session
DELETE {{apigateway}}/api/v1/sessions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/participants

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  CHAT
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get messages (last 50)
GET {{apigateway}}/api/v1/chat/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/messages

### Get messages (with pagination)
GET {{apigateway}}/api/v1/chat/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/messages?count=20&before=2025-01-01T00:00:00Z

### Send message
POST {{apigateway}}/api/v1/chat/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hey, where are you?"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  MARKERS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get markers for session
GET {{apigateway}}/api/v1/markers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Create marker
POST {{apigateway}}/api/v1/markers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "name": "Meeting point",
  "description": "At the forest entrance",
  "latitude": 49.2731,
  "longitude": 19.9806
}
